            "id": "4575642",
            "title": "Bank of America to redeem €1.5B senior notes due 2027",
            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\">Bank of America (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BAC\" title=\"Bank of America Corporation\">BAC</a></span>) plans to <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20475484-bank-of-america-announces-redemption-of-1500-000000-1_776-percent-fixed-floating-rate-senior\" target=\"_blank\" title=\" redeem \">redeem </a>on May 4, 2026 all €1.5B principal amount outstanding of its 1.776% Fixed/Floating Rate Senior Notes, due May 4, 2027.</li>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\">The notes were issued under the Bank of America Corporation U.S. $65B Euro Medium-Term Note Program.</li>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\">The redemption price will be equal to the optional redemption amount of €1,000 per €1,000 calculation amount (as specified in the Amended and Restated Final Terms dated May 8, 2018), plus accrued and unpaid interest to, but excluding, the redemption date of May 4, 2026.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\"></div>\n</body></html>",
            "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/assets/og_image_1200-29b2bfe1a595477db6826bd2126c63ac2091efb7ec76347a8e7f81ba17e3de6c.png",
            "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/news/4575642-bank-of-america-to-redeem-15b-senior-notes-due-2027",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-16 19:32:01",
            "source": "seekalpha",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "en"
        },
        {
            "id": "4575640",
            "title": "CoreWeave to offer $1B in additional 2031 notes",
            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\">CoreWeave (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CRWV\" title=\"CoreWeave, Inc.\">CRWV</a></span></span>) plans to offer $1B of 9.750% senior notes due 2031 in a private <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20475555-coreweave-announces-intention-to-offer-1000-million-of-9_750-percent-senior-notes-due-2031\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"offering\">offering</a>.</li>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\">The notes will be guaranteed by certain subsidiaries and will be issued as additional notes, alongside the company’s existing $1.75B of notes with the same terms.</li>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\">The firm plans to use the proceeds from the offering of the notes for general corporate purposes.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\"></div>\n</body></html>",
            "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/assets/og_image_1200-29b2bfe1a595477db6826bd2126c63ac2091efb7ec76347a8e7f81ba17e3de6c.png",
            "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/news/4575640-coreweave-to-offer-1b-in-additional-2031-notes",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-16 19:29:43",
            "source": "seekalpha",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "en"
        },
